  "detailed_description": "<strong>To meet my lost self</strong><br><br>This game is a 2D platformer.<br><br>But what makes it special is that you can't jump, and...<br><br><strong>you can turn the map around</strong>.<br><br>Below is a description of what the player can do.<br><br>1.movement, interactions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The left screen uses A, S, and D.<br>The right screen uses the left, down, and right keys.<br><br>The interaction is not only with the <strong>hold</strong> shown in the screenshot above, but other objects exist as well.<br><br>2. zoom out, rotate map<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The bottom center screen uses W, Up, LeftShift, and Space.<br><br>You can rotate under zoom as shown in the screenshot above,<br><br>For rotation, you can change the rotation speed by opening the settings.<br>And this is an important fact.<br><br>The last game I looked at<br><strong>50+ maps</strong>.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>To meet my lost self</strong><br><br>This game is a 2D platformer.<br><br>But what makes it special is that you can't jump, and...<br><br><strong>you can turn the map around</strong>.<br><br>Below is a description of what the player can do.<br><br>1.movement, interactions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ab63060590951072b5914c4dfa1c7c3a.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The left screen uses A, S, and D.<br>The right screen uses the left, down, and right keys.<br><br>The interaction is not only with the <strong>hold</strong> shown in the screenshot above, but other objects exist as well.<br><br>2. zoom out, rotate map<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/ed4ebb323bf6228419d6ce18e86bb9df.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.poster.avif?t=1711897751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.webm?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870900/extras/1de2ced47770dbea4071ca5b72f8095e.mp4?t=1711897751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The bottom center screen uses W, Up, LeftShift, and Space.<br><br>You can rotate under zoom as shown in the screenshot above,<br><br>For rotation, you can change the rotation speed by opening the settings.<br>And this is an important fact.<br><br>The last game I looked at<br><strong>50+ maps</strong>.",
